Appendix 11, page 1
FORM AND CONTENTS OF SUBPROJECT APPROVAL SUBMISSION
1.  The  subprojects  proposed  for  financing  under  the  Project  by  the  Ministry  of
Transport, Project Management Unit No. 5 (PMU-5) forming part of the Provincial Road
Sector Development Plan, will be submitted to the Asian Development Bank for approval.
The subproject approval submission will contain
(i)  cover letter;
(ii)  cover page;
(iii)  map of road and influence area;
(iv)  summary of road condition and proposed improvement (Table A11);
(v)  implementation schedule;
(vi)  environment  clearance  certificate  and  Asian  Development  Bank  initial
environmental examination/environmental assessment; and
(vii)  resettlement plan including ethnic minority development plan component (as
appropriate).
